 产品副总裁 Amit Fulay&lt;/a>; 解释道。 “无论您是参加电话会议以与客户联系还是讨论学校的秋季筹款活动，只需在加入会议时选择您的首选帐户即可。”&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：...&lt;/cite>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/20/24224507/microsoft-teams-work-single-personal-account -app-windows-mac-download&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/20/24224507/microsoft-teams-work-single-personal-account-app-windows-mac-download" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/20/24224507/microsoft-teams-work-single-personal-account-app-windows-mac-download</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry></feed>